description:
&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen for a Nursing Assistant at the Barnet Renal Dialysis Unit. The unit is part of the Nephrology department based at Royal Free London NHS Foundation in Hampstead. The unit is based at Barnet Hospital and is very near to the tube and bus services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working as a healthcare assistant is desirable but other relevant experience will be considered. Good communication skills, flexibility and a high standard of work are required for the post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are opportunities to develop skills and knowledge to complete hemodialysis competencies with a named mentor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Bindu Nair&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Senior Sister&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: bindu.nair2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 02082164955&lt;/p&gt;
